Fourth Department,

June, 1960

(June 1, 1960) In the Matter of Chester C. Gorski, Respondent, against Thomas J. Griffin et al., Appellants, and James R. Lawley et al., as Commissioners of Election, Erie County, Respondents.

Order unanimously affirmed, without costs of this appeal to any party. Application for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals granted. (Appeal from order of Erie Special Term.) Present-— Williams, P. J., Goldman, Halpern, McClusky and Henry, JJ.
